          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SOLST",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " For forward angle measurement, a",
                "telescope spectrometers is composed of 3 semi-",
                "conduction detector and CsI(Tl) to measure the",
                "projectile-like fragments from the reactions, and the",
                "distance between spectrometer and sample is 50 cm.",
                "The thickness of 3 semi-conduction detector is 130,",
                "1580 and 5000 um. For the middle-angle measurement,",
                "CsI(Tl) is set as 20 degree with beam direction and",
                "used to correlation measure the light particles."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "IOCH",
                "SOLST"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " For backward angle measurement, a",
                "telescope spectrometers is composed of gas ionization",
                "chamber and 3 semi-conduction position sensitive",
                "detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
